                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 312.52/607.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to Special
                        Agent <persName type="to">Silliman</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-05-29">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 29, 1915</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Department informed Mazatlan authorities have decreed expropriation Water Supply
                    Company, Mazatlan. At request Spanish Embassy, please confer with Spanish
                    Confidential Agent and exercise best efforts have this property protected
                    against unwarranted molestation.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Bryan.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
